    "However, AI and machine learning can help overcome these challenges.",
    "AI can accurately predict the properties of potential compounds, avoiding wasted time and money.",
    "It can also help develop new compounds by creating molecules with predicted success properties, improving drug discovery and development.",
    "AI can also eliminate repetitive tasks in assessing drug effectiveness.",
